language ESSENCE' 1.0

given n: int
given topMatrix: matrix indexed by [int(1..n), int(1..2*n)] of int(0..2*n)

$given rightMatrix: matrix indexed by [int(1..2*n), int(1..n)] of int(0..2*n)

find solution: matrix indexed by [int(1..2*n), int(1..2*n)] of int(1..0)

such that

forAll row: int(1..n).
  forAll col: int(1..2*n).
    (solution[row, col]=1)->(topMatrix[row, col])
